- I was going for a younger,
sexier, Vincent Price.

00:12.813 --> 00:14.282
- Okay, shut it.

00:14.315 --> 00:15.416
As much as I'd love
to talk about

00:15.449 --> 00:16.684
our wonderful show tonight--

00:16.717 --> 00:18.519
[sighs]
Whoopi Goldberg, Denis Leary,

00:18.552 --> 00:21.355
the amazing ventriloquist,
Jonathan Geffner,

00:21.389 --> 00:23.524
I actually have something
very serious

00:23.557 --> 00:26.794
and pressing
and somewhat urgent to discuss.

00:26.827 --> 00:30.398
- You finally got laid?
[laughter]

00:30.431 --> 00:32.433
- [laughs mockingly]
There's been an outbreak.

00:32.466 --> 00:34.102
- How serious of an outbreak?

00:34.135 --> 00:36.804
'Cause if it gets bad,
I do have cyanide pills

00:36.837 --> 00:38.806
in my desk drawer.
They are chewable,

00:38.839 --> 00:40.508
Very hard to find
on the deep web.

00:40.541 --> 00:43.077
- Absolutely it sounds extreme,
but it is the cleanest

00:43.111 --> 00:44.745
and easiest way to die.
- Okay.

00:44.778 --> 00:48.082
Everybody can kill themselves
during hiatus.

00:48.116 --> 00:50.118
The reason I look
a little glum

00:50.151 --> 00:51.819
is because we have
a lice outbreak.

00:51.852 --> 00:54.422
[all groaning]
All right, all right!

00:54.455 --> 00:56.390
It's not Ebola!

00:56.424 --> 00:58.326
[exhales]
But you all need to be treated.

00:58.359 --> 00:59.693
- Well, you might want
to start off with Marcus

00:59.727 --> 01:01.495
because his children
had lice all week.

01:01.529 --> 01:02.830
- You bitch!
- Dude!

01:02.863 --> 01:04.232
- What?
- That was a secret.

01:04.265 --> 01:06.500
- Marcus, patient zero!
- How dare you!

01:06.534 --> 01:08.369
- Don't worry,
the Lice Fairy is here.

01:08.402 --> 01:09.870
- Excuse me?
What did you call me?

01:09.903 --> 01:12.106
- The Jamaican ladies
to treat all of our scalps!

01:12.140 --> 01:13.407
- Oh, gotcha.

01:13.441 --> 01:16.244
- Um, I've had
two very bad experiences

01:16.277 --> 01:17.845
with Jamaican ladies
touching me.

01:17.878 --> 01:19.747
- This place is disgusting.

01:19.780 --> 01:22.216
I'd always knew I'd end up
getting something working here.

01:22.250 --> 01:24.152
- Which is why we all
need to be treated.

01:24.185 --> 01:26.554
- All right,
I have a time schedule

01:26.587 --> 01:28.822
of when everyone is going to
visit the Lice Fairy,

01:28.856 --> 01:30.491
so please see me after.

01:30.524 --> 01:33.161
- Yeah,
I think I see one.

01:33.194 --> 01:34.362
- What? Get it.

01:34.395 --> 01:35.563
- Kill him. Kill him!

01:35.596 --> 01:37.531
- Get it!
- [whimpers]

01:37.565 --> 01:40.501
[grunting, screaming]

01:42.870 --> 01:44.305
I got it.

01:44.338 --> 01:45.706
- From Studio 9B

01:45.739 --> 01:48.142
in the heart of New York City,

01:48.176 --> 01:50.611
it's "Nightcap with Jimmy."

01:50.644 --> 01:52.580
Tonight, we're
"Makin' Whoopee"

01:52.613 --> 01:55.249
with Whoopi Goldberg.

01:55.283 --> 01:59.287
Lovable Masshole Denis Leary.

01:59.320 --> 02:01.255
Renowned Jewish ventriloquist

02:01.289 --> 02:03.457
Jonathan Geffner.

02:03.491 --> 02:06.427
And now, the man who's
number five in the ratings,

02:06.460 --> 02:08.329
but number one in our hearts,

02:08.362 --> 02:10.664
here's Jimmy!

02:10.698 --> 02:14.668
*

02:14.702 --> 02:16.370
- We are in this small,
cramped room

02:16.404 --> 02:17.738
[whispers]
Because we have lice

02:17.771 --> 02:19.440
and nobody can
find out about it.

02:19.473 --> 02:20.874
We need to be quiet.

02:20.908 --> 02:22.810
Like Anne Frank quiet.

02:22.843 --> 02:24.678
- Yeah, yeah,
you got it bad.

02:24.712 --> 02:26.514
- I knew it.
- You know, if she has it,

02:26.547 --> 02:27.881
I probably have it
'cause I fell asleep

02:27.915 --> 02:29.917
in her lap last night
watching "Cupcake Wars."

02:29.950 --> 02:32.586
[all aww]
- Boy, that is sweet.

02:32.620 --> 02:34.688
And how long you all
been together for?

02:34.722 --> 02:36.557
- 2 years, 1 month,
13 days.

02:36.590 --> 02:38.492
- Oh. [chuckles]
- Oh, but...

02:38.526 --> 02:40.428
we're not--
we're not a couple.

02:40.461 --> 02:43.431
We don't...
- Oh.

02:43.464 --> 02:44.765
- Hey, you know,
when I was a kid,

02:44.798 --> 02:46.300
um, every time I had lice,

02:46.334 --> 02:47.768
my dad would soak my head
in kerosene.

02:47.801 --> 02:50.371
- I think it may have killed
more than just the lice.

02:50.404 --> 02:51.839
- In your medical opinion,

02:51.872 --> 02:54.342
uh, that treatment,
does it also...

02:54.375 --> 02:56.310
treat down here?

02:57.945 --> 02:59.513
My pubes?

02:59.547 --> 03:03.351
[lively music]

03:03.384 --> 03:04.818
- Oh, my God.
It's even worse than I thought.

03:04.852 --> 03:07.521
- I actually think
I look kind of hot.

03:07.555 --> 03:09.557
- I've never felt
so tough.

03:09.590 --> 03:11.425
- You all look hideous.

03:11.459 --> 03:13.261
- This is all your fault.
- Allegedly.

03:13.294 --> 03:14.662
- You guys don't get it.

03:14.695 --> 03:16.630
We are the fifth-rated
late night talk show.

03:16.664 --> 03:18.299
People find out
we have lice, that's it.

03:18.332 --> 03:19.333
We're done.
We're cancelled.

03:19.367 --> 03:20.901
- You're screwed.

03:20.934 --> 03:21.969
- It kind of looks like
we just got back

03:22.002 --> 03:23.637
from the Caribbean.

03:23.671 --> 03:25.339
- That's it.
That's what we're gonna say.

03:25.373 --> 03:26.907
We just got back
from the Caribbean.

03:26.940 --> 03:28.642
Don't tell Whoopi we have lice.

03:28.676 --> 03:29.943
- I can't wait
to get my cornrows.

03:29.977 --> 03:33.681
I have the perfect
facial structure for it.

03:33.714 --> 03:35.449
Sorry, Randy.

03:35.483 --> 03:37.651
And Penny.

03:37.685 --> 03:39.453
And Staci.
- I'm good.

03:39.487 --> 03:41.021
- Ehh...
- I'm cute.

03:41.054 --> 03:43.023
- [high-pitch] Ehh...
- Pretty.

03:43.056 --> 03:44.892
- [higher-pitched] Ehh...

03:44.925 --> 03:47.595
*

03:47.628 --> 03:48.862
- No, you can't.

03:48.896 --> 03:51.665
Because you can't cancel
the day of.

03:51.699 --> 03:53.967
