- Hey, Staci.

03:54.001 --> 03:55.903
I don't care!
He has to be on the sh--

03:55.936 --> 03:57.338
- Staci!

03:57.371 --> 03:59.607
- Maggie, hold on a second.
What, Todd?

03:59.640 --> 04:01.041
- Oh, uh, do you know where
Jimmy's peanut butter is?

04:01.074 --> 04:02.676
