Jimmy's peanut butter is.

04:02.710 --> 04:04.612
- Well, okay, well,
he told me to ask you

04:04.645 --> 04:06.314
'cause you know
where everything is.

04:06.347 --> 04:08.582
- Maggie, listen to me.
I understand that he's sick,

04:08.616 --> 04:10.451
but you cannot cancel--

04:10.484 --> 04:11.652
Maggie!

04:11.685 --> 04:13.521
[shouts]
Maggie!

04:13.554 --> 04:15.423
Oh!
- Is Denis Leary sick?

04:15.456 --> 04:16.857
- Well, his manager
says he is.

04:16.890 --> 04:18.726
- No! God!
Jimmy loves Denis!

04:18.759 --> 04:20.361
We got to get
Denis Leary on the show!

04:20.394 --> 04:21.929
- I know!
- All right, well,

04:21.962 --> 04:23.464
Jimmy didn't prepare anything,
'cause, you know

04:23.497 --> 04:24.898
he can always wing it
with Denis, so...

04:24.932 --> 04:26.667
