does prepare

04:26.700 --> 04:29.337
for his interviews?
- No, he doesn't. [laughs]

04:29.370 --> 04:30.604
So you don't know
where the peanut butter is?

04:30.638 --> 04:32.340
- Oh!
Check his bottom drawer!

04:32.373 --> 04:34.575
- Bottom drawer.
God, yes!

04:34.608 --> 04:36.477
- Oh, my God,
I can feel them hatching.

04:36.510 --> 04:38.446
- Oh, God, the Lice Fairy
is still here.

04:40.781 --> 04:42.416
- Ugh!

04:42.450 --> 04:43.784
Hey, um,

04:43.817 --> 04:45.919
you--you know where
the ventriloquist

04:45.953 --> 04:47.755
put the puppet thing?

04:47.788 --> 04:50.391
- Oh, you mean Ezra?

04:50.424 --> 04:52.793
He's not technically a puppet,

04:52.826 --> 04:55.763
he's a dummy
and he's in dressing room #3.

04:55.796 --> 04:57.731
Did you want to meet him?
- No!

04:57.765 --> 04:59.567
Nope. Nope. Nope.
Nope. Nope.

04:59.600 --> 05:01.602
He doesn't have access
to the whole building, right?

05:01.635 --> 05:03.904
- Oh, well, he is a guest,

05:03.937 --> 05:05.839
but he's not a person,

05:05.873 --> 05:07.841
but he lives in a suitcase.

05:07.875 --> 05:09.710
- The suitcase has locks
on it, right?

05:09.743 --> 05:11.979
So he--he can't get out.
- I don't think so.

05:12.012 --> 05:13.347
Why?

05:13.381 --> 05:14.648
- [scoffs]
No reason.

05:14.682 --> 05:16.617
It's just, you know,
I don't want...

05:16.650 --> 05:18.386
to surprise him.
I don't want him...

05:18.419 --> 05:19.553
to surprise me.

05:19.587 --> 05:21.522
You know,
it's just one of th--

05:24.458 --> 05:26.494
Just one of those things.
You know what I mean?

05:26.527 --> 05:32.900
*

05:32.933 --> 05:35.135
- Oh, Whoopi.
Big fan.

05:35.168 --> 05:37.004
- Thanks.

05:37.037 --> 05:38.706
I think.

05:38.739 --> 05:40.408
- Oh, Whoopi Goldberg,
we are so excited

05:40.441 --> 05:41.509
to have you
on the show.

05:41.542 --> 05:43.877
- Okay, so is this

05:43.911 --> 05:46.046
some sort of...
diversity thing?

05:46.079 --> 05:48.015
To make me feel
more comfortable

05:48.048 --> 05:49.617
being black and everything?

05:49.650 --> 05:51.719
- No, no, no, no, no.
#BlackLivesMatter.

05:51.752 --> 05:54.455
Um, no, we were on
a company cruise.

05:54.488 --> 05:57.024
- You know that doesn't make
this any less racist?

05:57.057 --> 05:58.726
Right?

05:58.759 --> 06:01.061
- Can I offer you guys
some freshly-sliced watermelon?

06:01.094 --> 06:02.996
- Don't mind if I do.

06:03.030 --> 06:04.865
- Fresh watermelon,
Ms. Whoopi?

06:04.898 --> 06:08.168
- Sure. 'Cause who
doesn't like watermelon?

06:08.201 --> 06:09.903
- Mm-hmm.

06:09.937 --> 06:11.672
- You know, I gotta tell you,
this is really

06:11.705 --> 06:13.541
making me
a little uncomfortable.

06:13.574 --> 06:15.409
I just feel like
maybe "Nightcap"

06:15.443 --> 06:16.777
is not the place I should be.

06:16.810 --> 06:18.779
- No, no, no, no, no,
Whoopi.

06:18.812 --> 06:21.782
Please don't walk out.
- I gotta think about this.

06:21.815 --> 06:24.518
Do you think we could
take the watermelon to my room?

06:24.552 --> 06:25.986
- Yes!
- A safer environment.

06:26.019 --> 06:27.421
Absolutely.
- Yeah. Yeah.

06:27.455 --> 06:28.656
- Let's go.

06:28.689 --> 06:30.491
I've always felt
this show was racist.

06:30.524 --> 06:31.725
- [strained] Grady!
- I know.

06:31.759 --> 06:33.594
- [exhales sharply]

06:33.627 --> 06:34.995
- Well, this is a pickle.

06:35.028 --> 06:37.064
- Listen to me,
if we lose Whoopi--

06:37.097 --> 06:39.099
we've already lost Denis Leary
because he's sick,

06:39.132 --> 06:41.702
we're gonna have 40 minutes
of a ventriloquist.

06:41.735 --> 06:43.737
- But the ventriloquist
is so good.

06:43.771 --> 06:46.607
- Not for 40 minutes.
[phone dings]

06:46.640 --> 06:48.676
What?
Did you see your reflection?

06:48.709 --> 06:50.478
- Whoa.
No, no, no.

06:50.511 --> 06:53.146
So my friend who works
on Denis' show

06:53.180 --> 06:56.817
said that Denis
is at work today and looks fine.

06:56.850 --> 06:59.887
- You have a friend?
- She's an online friend.

06:59.920 --> 07:03.223
She says that he also baked
banana bread for the crew.

07:03.256 --> 07:05.993
- Asshole!
You know what?

07:06.026 --> 07:08.161
I'm gonna go down
to Denis Leary's set

07:08.195 --> 07:11.899
