- No.

08:21.635 --> 08:23.303
Well, yes and no.

08:23.336 --> 08:24.905
Look,
I know Denis Leary's trailer

08:24.938 --> 08:26.740
is around here somewhere.
I'm trying to find it.

08:26.774 --> 08:28.175
- Oh, I know where he is!

08:28.208 --> 08:30.611
My friend told me
he's around the corner.

08:30.644 --> 08:31.812
Go get him, tiger!

08:31.845 --> 08:33.113
- Copy that.

08:33.146 --> 08:35.749
- You tell them that
the situation's changed.

08:35.783 --> 08:37.818
Oh, fuck.
God damn it.

08:37.851 --> 08:39.019
What?
- Oh, fucking Leary.

08:39.052 --> 08:40.253
- What?
- Oh, my God, look at your hair.

08:40.287 --> 08:41.755
- I can't believe you
came down here.

