Tonight at 7:00?

09:17.090 --> 09:18.992
- Can I explain something?
- You mother...

09:19.026 --> 09:20.761
- Let me explain something
to you,

09:20.794 --> 09:23.296
this--this is--
I'm not sick.

09:23.330 --> 09:25.799
I don't--I don't like to brag
about my charity stuff.

09:25.833 --> 09:29.069
So what I'm doing is
I'm taking a couple of sick kids

09:29.102 --> 09:31.104
to the--I am.

09:31.138 --> 09:33.306
