it's like--

09:40.113 --> 09:41.381
you know what I mean?
It's a big thing.

09:41.414 --> 09:43.784
- You can't eat pork
if you have lupus?

09:43.817 --> 09:45.118
- I don't think you can eat--
there's certain things

09:45.152 --> 09:46.353
you can't eat. Yeah.
I mean, I don't know

09:46.386 --> 09:48.021
everything about it,
I'm just--Listen,

09:48.055 --> 09:49.990
I don't like to brag about it,
so I said I was sick,

09:50.023 --> 09:51.224
I didn't want to mention
sick kids.

09:51.258 --> 09:52.926
- All right,
so it's at 7:00, okay?

09:52.960 --> 09:54.895
You can still--
You can still do our show

09:54.928 --> 09:57.297
and make it there by 7:00.
- Yes, but...

09:57.330 --> 10:00.100
there's a...
pre-game skate.

10:00.133 --> 10:01.802
Which is--
- You're gonna skate

10:01.835 --> 10:04.004
