- It's a lupus, uh...

10:04.037 --> 10:05.906
related skate.
- Okay, you know what, Denis?

10:05.939 --> 10:07.875
- And that's at 6:00.
- You're a grown man.

10:07.908 --> 10:10.377
So why don't we just say,
you do the show,

10:10.410 --> 10:11.912
you'll be there by 7:00.

10:11.945 --> 10:13.046
