all the sick kids

10:13.080 --> 10:14.848
with you to the show.
Okay?

10:14.882 --> 10:16.884
- I-I'm not sure the sick kids
will want to come to the show.

10:16.917 --> 10:18.251
[stammers]
- All right, well,

10:18.285 --> 10:20.220
