10:20.253 --> 10:22.756
Please.

10:22.790 --> 10:24.224
- All right, I'll do it.
- You will?

10:24.257 --> 10:25.859
- I'll do it. Yeah.
- Oh, my God.

10:25.893 --> 10:27.260
- All right.
- Oh, my God, you're the best.

10:27.294 --> 10:28.929
- Okay.
- Oh, my God.

10:28.962 --> 10:30.898
If you weren't married...
- All right, if--

10:30.931 --> 10:33.233
Well, I'm very married,
so...Yeah.

10:33.266 --> 10:35.302
All right.

10:35.335 --> 10:39.372
"Nightcap" fuckin'
piece of shit that show is.

10:39.406 --> 10:42.309
- I got him.
- Yay, that's such good news.

10:42.342 --> 10:44.878
