some good news too.

10:44.912 --> 10:46.814
I got us a ride back
to the studio.

10:46.847 --> 10:48.749
- [gasps]
Oh, my gosh, Penny!

10:48.782 --> 10:51.184
This is so fun.

10:51.218 --> 10:54.054
Oh!
